Narrative:
As a player
I want Account balance to be displayed in the bottom area of the Bet slip
so that I know the amount of money that I have in my account to place wagers


Scenario: Account Balance is displayed in Bet slip
Given a player loggedIn and navigate to live betting page
When CWF provides account balance
And Bet slip mode is activated
Then Account balance will be displayed in the bottom area of the Bet slip
